ion of the jet and the peculiar emission\nmorphology are far from being understood and require deeper observations as\nwell as a detailed modeling of the interaction of a jet with its surroundings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Oct 2006 12:21:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
